      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "马岱引姜维同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00002",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "量小非君子，无毒不丈夫。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00003",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "马备征鞍将挂袍，柳梢之上月轮高。男儿要挂封侯印，腰下长悬带血刀。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00004",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "本帅姓姜名维，字伯约。自从诸葛丞相归天之后，所托中原一事，本帅朝夕在怀。今奉皇太后娘娘懿旨，带领四十五万人马，恢复中原。昨日探马报道：魏国命司马师带领倾国人马，前来与本帅交锋。且喜天色已晚，不免去到土台之上，观看那贼营盘。马岱！",
      "text_length": 114
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00005",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马岱"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00006",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "掌灯伺候。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00007",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马岱"
      ],
      "text": "哦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00008",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "俺姜维离虎座忙出宝帐，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00009",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "迈步儿出营来细观端详。叫马岱掌银灯随定前往，",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00010",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马岱"
      ],
      "text": "哦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00011",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "一霎时日坠西玉兔东方。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00012",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖起初更鼓〗。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00013",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "听谯楼打罢了初更鼓响，待本帅坐雕鞍细表其详：想当初先帝爷桃园结义，初起手破黄巾四海名扬。曹孟德引见帝宗谱查考，靖王后景帝孙汉室堂堂。献帝爷称皇叔才把兵掌，曹阿瞒威权重扰乱朝纲。因此上受密诏剿灭奸党，事不谨将机关洩露宣扬。先帝爷弃皇城连夜奔走，曹孟德带人马赶出许昌。将关公围困在高坡之上，有一个张文远苦苦说降。劝关公若降曹封侯拜将，好一位美髯公议事三桩。降汉朝受爵禄不降曹党，寻兄长虽千里不论何方。如不然与曹瞒共决死战，明桃园结义情地久天长。谁知那曹孟德随口应允，奏献帝受爵禄汉寿亭侯威赫显扬。探马报先帝爷兵归袁术，因此上辞曹瞒将金印悬挂高粱。张文远带药酒灞桥阻挡，过五关斩六将四海名扬。渡黄河斩秦琪逆贼命丧，古城下斩蔡阳血染沙场。先帝爷同翼德迎接城上，兄弟们重相会喜气杨扬。运不通时不至跋涉奔走，到隆中访诸葛三顾草堂。待英雄礼贤才宽洪大量，谁知那曹孟德任意猖狂。挟天子令诸侯群僚胆丧，文武臣一个个弃职归乡。",
      "text_length": 403
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00014",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "我想曹操名虽汉相实乃汉贼，说来令人可恨也。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00015",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "先帝爷势力微奔守夏口，待天时凑机缘重整朝纲。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00016",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "先帝爷乃仁德之君，不忍夺取同宗基业，苦守夏口。谁知那刘琮孺子，听信母言，将荆襄九郡，献与曹操，因此先帝爷与先生商议道：大丈夫必须要自立基业才是。先生说道：且待天时，自有机缘，主公不必忧虑。",
      "text_length": 94
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00017",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "曹瞒贼得荆襄猖狂越甚，逼吾主奔新野百姓遭殃。弃樊城败当阳英雄气丧，赖先生壮威风，施仁政，爱良民，居夏口，招军买马聚草屯粮。",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00018",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "不想那曹操据了荆襄九郡，统领八十三万人马大下江南。那东吴孙权，心意不定，即命鲁肃过江探听曹兵虚实。好一个诸葛先生，与先帝爷商议：鲁肃此来，正合吾意，待我借东吴之力成自己之功，夺得汉室疆土以为创业之根本。",
      "text_length": 101
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00019",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "曹孟德带人马八十三万，隔大江于北岸扎下营盘。南屏山借东风先生逃走，赵子龙射蓬索保他回还。有关公华容道义释曹操，因此上那奸贼得返中原。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00020",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "吾主得了荆州一带地方，那孙权心中不忿，道我东吴折了许多粮草。反被孔明就中取事，又失许多城池。因此与周郎商议定下美人之计，诓哄吾主过江老死东吴。谁知孔明先生预先准备三个锦囊，付与赵云命他相机行事，先帝才得脱离虎口。后来孙权要取荆州，勒逼鲁肃过江面议，那鲁肃设下赴会之计，置备酒宴诓哄关公过江饮酒。酒席筵前索取荆州，若还不允即行杀害。可见智谋之士断不可少，威勇之人亦不可无吓！",
      "text_length": 186
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00021",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "恨只恨昔日里放走曹操，到今日伐中原费尽心田。站立在土台上用目观看，又只见松树内雾气漫漫。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00022",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "马岱！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00023",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马岱"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00024",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "前面雾气漫漫，就是那贼的营盘么？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00025",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马岱"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00026",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02004053_e00027",
      "play_id": "02004053",
      "scene_id": "02004053_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "姜维"
      ],
      "text": "观东方铁笼山山势非大，观西方白虎山并无深渊；观南方棋盘山山峰奇险，观北方平阳地可把营安。军师爷在西蜀预伏八阵，受先帝托孤重保定江山。出祁山剿汉贼遵奉遗命，俺姜维秉忠心恢复中原。一来是成先生胸中之愿，二来是奉国太密旨森严。因此上趁黑夜把贼营窥探，为将者胸腹内广有机缘。观天文察地理掌中细算，决胜负全凭着韬略当先。斩大将虏三军神机妙算，管叫他军马队尽受摧残。只杀得众贼兵魂飞魄散，早成功报主恩奏凯回还。",
      "text_length": 199
